            <p n="a#2" xml:space="preserve">Ku<ex>n</ex>gør jæc th<ex>et</ex> allæ mæ<ex>n</ex> næ<ex>rwæren</ex>de oc <app><lem>ko<ex>m</ex>me<ex>n</ex>de</lem><rdg wit="#A"><q>ko<ex>m</ex>mede</q>, A</rdg></app> at jæc vedh<ex>e</ex>rkænnis mik m<ex>eth</ex> th<ex>e</ex>ttæ mit wpnæ b<ex>re</ex>ff
